➜宽体思域内藏着小丑，深夜出没请避而远之！
http://www.sohu.com/a/366231811_163713	20665
<p>最近两年，十代思域的案例可谓非常之多，无论是在车友聚会上，还是在改装展会上，都能见到各种各样的改装车。正是由于太多人玩了，所以车子没有太多亮点的话，很难给人留下深刻的印象。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/c58da2408aa747719ecf5ef9e8c293a3.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/2a9a25ebb46f4338b1e4c22ed5998aaa.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>今天我们和大家介绍的这辆思域，除了有点绿色的外观和宽体之外，当我们打开引擎盖，还能发现另一个特色，那就是巨大的小丑涂装。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/f139403045494c95ad886dd55ea31296.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/1cfb7d21bb294184abc46aa2969908ea.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>看过《小丑》的朋友都能发现，这是一部风格大胆的电影，很多人都能从中获得不一样的感悟。而本文的车主James另辟蹊径，将小丑的元素融合到了改装上面，给人不一样的视觉体验。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/934033d0febc407eaedbd5363030dec2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/7f07319d35344ba7982ecd48da0b034c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>其实在拥有这辆车的最初阶段，James只是改装了气动避震。简简单单的效果，虽然看起来很舒服，但是却并不能满足他对改装的追求。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/6aca1db6948b430c8918f5570b00c4a1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/973d967aea46426b9c913d623d69d563.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/4dcf7166de5a490b82cac11fec59a8e6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>于是，不甘平凡的他决定加装一套宽体套件。前后翼子板和后车门均被进行了切割处理，与此同时，前后保险杠和侧裙也进行了相应的修改。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/daee6a9cb1664463b86627e0400b204b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/4829c9c15d6048aebe3c962e489d460f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/db5c85dea5934515b42e498e0532885d.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>充满战斗感的宽体和SD定制抛边轮毂，让这辆原本就改了气动的思域做到了大王的姿态。不过呢，这时候引擎盖却不见了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/207966ae16764e3daea50e15f5593c18.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/7192803a363b4144a8cec745be656cb7.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>原来是拿去制作小丑的涂装，而从细节来看，小丑的眼神、头发、嘴唇、手里拿着的扑克牌等都做得非常形象逼真。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/3304ff9cbaca466abe09671634f47be4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/a84e490cc2d648e692c7420ae74afad5.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/2cfa37501233481bb44dd46a89f0cb6b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/c5d9b4b2852c421e948496ace5c811a6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>如果晚上开出去的话，打开引擎盖停在那里，相信很多人老远看到之后，都会绕着路走，因为确实有点吓人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/6f1bd78112cb4ea6915069c48bad11a6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/8fc5bfeeb49d4dd7b6c7795f24d32d22.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>当引擎盖关起来的时候，仿佛让人忘记了昨天晚上的经历，所有的一切又回到了正常。帅气的思域大王，安静在停在路边，等候别人的欣赏。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/bb1f25cb49c043e691abd75a14c7fbd6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/6afd5c4e06f34467b584d9a8d45fd17e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/be3465de250a4d9c8e4500ab7b73929a.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>看完今天的这个案例，相信会给你一些视觉上的冲击。如果是你的话，想在引擎盖内做出什么样的涂装呢？欢迎在留言区告诉我们！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/ee854a92ab024dfdb528919e8311b6c6.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20200111/100b55eb6d284b119449a7df943d2e5b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
